flowRoot.flowPara: Each color represents the detector at various displacement relative to a single point. A scope image was saved every 0.050 $\mu$m.
The signal circled in black belongs to the $TEM_{00}$ mode since it has no nodes.
The signal in green has a node at around 0.200$\mu$m. This is not the peak we want to maximize. It could possibly be $TEM_{10}$
